ngram\": \"his fourth Olympics\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His brother admitted: \\\"'I think Jonny's been unhappy with his results.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His brother\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"Jonny\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"his results\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would have liked to perform a lot better but I guess he's still in contention and we will see what the selectors say.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"the selectors\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we have three very good medal chances in the three triathlon events and a very good team so that's very exciting.\\\"\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three very good medal chances\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"the three triathlon events\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"a very good team\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These days Brownlee plies his trade on the inaugural T100 World Tour, which sees 20 of the world's best professional triathletes battle over a season of 8 breakneck 100km races in iconic locations around the globe.\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"score\": 0.9859007480295722, \"rank\": 0.014282954520393007, \"text\": \"Brownlee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his trade\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"the inaugural T100 World Tour\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2701}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best professional triathletes battle\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"a season\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"8 breakneck 100km races\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"iconic locations\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With equal prize money for men and women, $3M has been doled out in athlete contracts with a huge end-of-season payout total of $2M shared between all 20 athletes.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"equal prize money\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete contracts\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"season\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"$2M\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"all 20 athletes\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's fantastic that prize money is coming into a sport like long-distance triathlon,\\\" said Brownlee, who will race at the third stage of the World Tour in San Francisco this weekend.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3106, \"end\": 3114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"score\": 0.9859007480295722, \"rank\": 0.014282954520393007, \"text\": \"Brownlee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\"}, {\"begin\": 3170, \"end\": 3183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco\", \"score\": 0.9999586943867996, \"rank\": 4.107480227289903e-05, \"text\": \"San Francisco\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"prize